        <header>
            <h1>奶香黄金芝麻小餐包</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">松软香甜的自发粉小餐包，金黄的外皮裹满芝麻，奶香浓郁，制作简单，适合家庭烘焙新手！</p>
            
            <div class="recipe-meta">
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    <span>准备时间: 30分钟</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-temperature-high"></i>
                    <span>烘烤时间: 18分钟</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-bread-slice"></i>
                    <span>份量: 12个小餐包</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
                    <span>难度: 简单</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="content">
            <section class="section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> 所需工具</h2>
                <div class="ingredient-category">
                    <ul class="ingredient-list">
                        <li>电子秤</li>
                        <li>大号搅拌盆</li>
                        <li>烘焙油纸</li>
                        <li>烤盘（约28×28cm）</li>
                        <li>烤箱</li>
                        <li>刷子</li>
                        <li>保鲜膜</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-shopping-basket"></i> 所需食材</h2>
                <div class="ingredients-grid">
                    <div class="ingredient-category">
                        <h3>主面团</h3>
                        <ul class="ingredient-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">自发小麦粉</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">650克</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">温牛奶（约35°C）</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">250毫升</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">细砂糖</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">50克</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">鸡蛋（室温）</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">1个</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">植物油</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">25毫升</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">盐</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">2克</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="ingredient-category">
                        <h3>表面装饰</h3>
                        <ul class="ingredient-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">牛奶（刷表面用）</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">适量</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">全蛋液（1个鸡蛋打散）</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">适量</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">黑芝麻</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">适量</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="ingredient-category">
                        <h3>馅料（可选）</h3>
                        <ul class="ingredient-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="ingredient-name">豆沙/奶黄/椰蓉馅</span>
                                <span class="ingredient-amount">约200克</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-list-ol"></i> 详细步骤</h2>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">混合湿料</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>在搅拌盆中倒入250毫升温牛奶。加入25毫升植物油、1个鸡蛋、50克细砂糖和2克盐。搅拌均匀至糖盐溶解。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-blender"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">加入自发粉</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>将650克自发小麦粉加入湿料中。搅拌至无干粉，形成粗糙面团。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-weight"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">揉面</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>将面团移到操作台，揉8-10分钟至光滑有弹性。判断标准：面团柔软不粘手，能拉出较厚的膜。调整：太粘可加少量油（5毫升内），太干可加几滴牛奶。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-hand-rock"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">分割与整形</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>将面团分成12等份（每份约75克），揉圆。松弛10分钟后，包入馅料（可选），再次揉圆。收口朝下放在铺有油纸的烤盘上，间隔3厘米。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-cut"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">5</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">醒发</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>烤盘放入烤箱，旁边放一碗热水。关闭烤箱门，醒发60-70分钟至1.5倍大。判断标准：轻按表面缓慢回弹。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-temperature-high"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">6</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">烘烤（总时间18分钟）</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <div class="baking-steps">
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">预热</span>烤箱：上火175°C/下火165°C（家用烤箱170°C）。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">第一次刷牛奶</span>：在醒发好的面团表面刷一层薄牛奶。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">放入烤箱</span>，设置13分钟计时。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">烤3分钟后</span>：取出快速刷第二次牛奶，放回烤箱继续烤。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">烤13分钟结束</span>：取出，刷全蛋液，撒黑芝麻（可选）。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">调整温度</span>：烤箱调至上火160°C/下火145°C（或整体150°C）。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">继续烤5分钟</span>：放回烤箱烤5分钟，总时间18分钟。</div>
                                    <div class="baking-step"><span class="time-highlight">判断熟度</span>：表面金黄，牙签插入中心无粘连。</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-oven"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">7</div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">冷却与保存</div>
                            <div class="step-details">
                                <p>立即将面包移至烤网，完全冷却后密封保存。室温可保存2-3天，冷冻可保存1个月。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step-image">
                            <i class="fas fa-wind"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 成功秘诀与小贴士</h2>
                <div class="tips-grid">
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                            <h3>时间把控</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>使用计时器，严格按照3分钟、13分钟的时间节点操作。刷牛奶和蛋液时动作要快，每次操作控制在30秒内，避免烤箱降温过多。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-thermometer-half"></i>
                            <h3>温度调整</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>若烤箱不能独立控温，全程170°C烤13分钟，刷蛋液后150°C烤5分钟。最后5分钟注意观察，避免上色过深。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                            <h3>自发粉特性</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>自发粉已含膨松剂，不需再加酵母，开封后需密封防潮。使用自发粉揉面时间可稍短，无需追求"手套膜"，光滑有弹性即可。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-cloud-sun"></i>
                            <h3>醒发控制</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>冬天可延长醒发至90分钟，夏天可能只需50分钟，主要看状态而非死守时间。发酵至1.5倍大，轻按缓慢回弹即可。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-cookie-bite"></i>
                            <h3>无馅版本</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>可不包馅，在分割后直接揉圆，或在面团中加入葡萄干、蔓越莓等果干增加风味。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="tip-card">
                        <div class="tip-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-snowflake"></i>
                            <h3>复热方法</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>冷冻面包取出后，表面喷水，150°C烤5-8分钟即可恢复松软口感。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
        
